蔡懷恩<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.t-classical.com/portfolio-posts/huai-en-tsai-info |title = 長號演奏家 蔡懷恩 |author = 王奇恩 |date =2011-01-29|publisher = 台灣古典音樂網 |language = 中文 |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723074532/http://www.t-classical.com/portfolio-posts/huai-en-tsai-info |dead-url = no }}</ref> (1980年8月21日- ) 生於[[台中市|台中市]][[烏日區|烏日區]]。旅美[[長號|長號]]演奏家<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://campus.chinatimes.com/20170224005300-262301 |title = 南華大學旅美長號音樂家 蔡懷恩留學經驗談 |author = 劉家均 |date =2017-02-24|publisher = 中時電子報 |language = 中文 |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723094432/https://campus.chinatimes.com/20170224005300-262301 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。祖籍台中清水，其高祖父為日治時期台灣社會運動領袖[[蔡惠如|蔡惠如]]。

==學歷==
蔡懷恩畢業於[[臺北市立成功高級中學|臺北市立成功高級中學]]及[[東吳大學|東吳大學]][[音樂學系|音樂學系]]。2006年取得美國[[約翰霍普金斯大學|約翰霍普金斯大學]][[琵琶第音樂學院|琵琶第音樂學院]][[碩士|碩士]]，2012年取得該校音樂藝術博士學位<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://peabodyinstitute.wordpress.com/2018/10/15/peabody-alumni-perform-at-celebration/ |title = Peabody Alumni Perform At Celebration |author = Peabody Institute News |date = 2018-10-15 |publisher = The Peabody Post |language = EN |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200724043242/https://peabodyinstitute.wordpress.com/2018/10/15/peabody-alumni-perform-at-celebration/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，是該校繼Kenneth Hanlon、Brad Edwards 之後第三位長號演奏家獲得該學位。

==經歷==
在台求學期間，曾任職於[[台北市立交響樂團|台北市立交響樂團]]附設管樂團及台北市民交響樂團，並於國防部示範樂隊服役。2016-2018年任美國[[弗羅斯特堡_(馬里蘭州)|弗羅斯特堡 (馬里蘭州)]]州立大學夏季音樂院銅管暨室內樂教師<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.broadwayworld.com/baltimore/article/Frostburg-State-University-To-Offer-Summer-Music-Academy-20170223 |title = Frostburg State University To Offer Summer Music Academy |author = BWW News Desk |date =2017-02-23|publisher = Broadway World Baltimore |language = EN |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723074219/https://www.broadwayworld.com/baltimore/article/Frostburg-State-University-To-Offer-Summer-Music-Academy-20170223 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.times-news.com/news/local_news/diverse-group-of-students-improves-abilities-at-summer-music-academy/article_38fed90b-997b-554f-9028-7616f492e9b9.html |title = Diverse group of students improves abilities at Summer Music Academy |author = Makea Luzader |date =2017-08-05|publisher = Cumberland Time-News |language = EN |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723063259/https://www.times-news.com/news/local_news/diverse-group-of-students-improves-abilities-at-summer-music-academy/article_38fed90b-997b-554f-9028-7616f492e9b9.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。目前任美國華盛頓普羅亞特室內樂團長號首席<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.pacodc.org/#orchestra-personnel |title = Personnel The Artists of PACO |author = Pro Arte Chamber Orchestra of Washington Team |date = 2015 |publisher = Pro Arte Chamber Orchestra of Washington |language = EN |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723063259/https://www.pacodc.org/#orchestra-personnel |dead-url = no }}</ref>
，並任教於美國中西大學華盛頓校區。蔡懷恩現為美國愛德華長號代言藝術家<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.edwards-instruments.com/artists/huai-en-tsai/|title = Huai-En Tsai Principal Trombonist, ProArte Chamber Orchestra of Washington|author = Lexi Wachtveitl|date = 2019|publisher = Edwards Instruments Co.,|language = EN|accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723071010/https://www.edwards-instruments.com/artists/huai-en-tsai/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2019年11月，蔡懷恩赴宜蘭演奏，紀念美國[[羅克維爾_(馬里蘭州)|羅克維爾 (馬里蘭州)]]與[[宜蘭市|宜蘭市]]締結姊妹市。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E8%99%9F%E5%98%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%8F%AF%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83-21%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E6%BC%94-160000559.html |title = 長號嘉年華音樂會 21日開演 |author = 董秀雲 |date = 2019-11-18 |publisher = 台灣新生報 |language = 中文 |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723063258/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E8%99%9F%E5%98%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%8F%AF%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83-21%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E6%BC%94-160000559.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.travelnews.tw/news/%E8%88%87%E5%A7%90%E5%A6%B9%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4%E8%B7%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81/ |title = 與姐妹市的一場跨國音樂交流 |author = 宜蘭新聞網新聞中心 |date = 2019-11-18 |publisher = 宜蘭新聞網 |language = 中文 |accessdate =2020-07-22|archive-date = 2020-07-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200723080229/https://www.travelnews.tw/news/%E8%88%87%E5%A7%90%E5%A6%B9%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4%E8%B7%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%9C%E8%98%AD%E5%B8%82%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B4%9B%E5%85%8B%E7%B6%AD%E7%88%BE%E5%B8%82%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E9%95%B7%E8%99%9F%E5%98%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%8F%AF%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83-160000393.html |title = 宜蘭市與美國洛克維爾市推出長號嘉年華音樂會 |author = 董秀雲 |date = 2019-11-20 |publisher = 台灣新生報 |language = 中文 |accessdate =2020-07-22|arc